SUMMARY:DALRYMPLE BAY FINANCE PTY LTD — Group Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Presenters: Michael Riches (Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer)\, Stephanie Commons (Chief Financial Officer). Time in other zones: 14:15-15:15 AEDT / 11:15-12:15 SIN/HKG / 12:15-13:15 JPN. Registration: https://evercall.co/oacc/73057. Replay available for nine days via the above link.\nIssuer: DALRYMPLE BAY FINANCE PTY LTD\nRoadshow: https://dealroadshow.com/e/DBI2026 OR Visit: https://dealroadshow.com and enter the deal entry code: DBI2026\n\nDeal context:\nDalrymple Bay Finance Pty Ltd is making its debut in the Australian dollar bond market with a 5-year senior secured fixed rate bond. The deal is at the roadshow stage\, with investor meetings scheduled across Sydney\, Melbourne\, Singapore\, and Hong Kong from March 2–5\, 2026. No pricing\, size\, or spread guidance has been provided at this stage.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
